                    <li> Click "Know your vehicle details"</li>
                    <li> Enter registration number</li>
                    <li> Scroll to see <span class="font-weight-700">insurance status</span>, policy expiry, and insurer name</li>
                </ol>

                <h3 class="subheading">Through Insurance Provider Portals:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Login using policy number</li>
                    <li>View or download policy documents</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="subheading">Using mParivahan:</h3>
